an style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">false</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> })</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">// false</span></span></code></pre>\",\"id\":\"pages/docs/utilities/isHex.md#optionsstrict\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nType: boolean\\nDefault: true\\n\\nWhen enabled, checks if the value strictly consists of only hex characters (&quot;0x[0-9a-fA-F]*&quot;).\\nWhen disabled, checks if the value loosely matches hex format (value.startsWith(&#x27;0x&#x27;)).\\nisHex(&#x27;0xlol&#x27;, { strict: false })\\n// true\\n \\nisHex(&#x27;0xlol&#x27;, { strict: true })\\n// false\\n \\nisHex(&#x27;lol&#x27;, { strict: false })\\n// false\",\"title\":\"options.strict\",\"titles\":[\"isHex\",\"Parameters\"]}]}}"
